---
import './style.scss';
---

<div class="skills">
    <div class="row heading">
        Skills I Have
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="skill">
            <div class="title">
                Front-end Development
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                Skilled in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, with expertise in frameworks like React, NextJS, AstroJS for crafting engaging user interfaces
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill">
            <div class="title">
                Back-end Development
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                Proficient in server-side languages like Golang, Python, Java, Node.JS specializing in building scalable APIs and robust back-end systems that serve millions of users.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="skill">
            <div class="title">
                Database Management
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                Experienced in PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, and other NoSQL databases, ensuring efficient data storage and retrieval for applications. Choosing the right database for the need is probably the most crucial decision of a project.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill">
            <div class="title">
                Full-Stack Frameworks
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                Expertise in MERN stacks, and Next.JS leveraging pre-built components for rapid development and seamless integration
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="skill">
            <div class="title">
                Cloud Infrastructure
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                Familiar with cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud for deploying and scaling applications, utilizing services like EC2, ECS and ELB for small to large scale deployments
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill">
            <div class="title">
                DevOps
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                Knowledgeable in Docker, GitHub Actions, and CI/CD pipelines for automating build, test, and deployment processes, ensuring efficient software delivery.

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
